==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Somnambulistic
<hw>Som*nam`bu*lis"tic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or
pertaining to a somnambulist or somnambulism; affected by somnambulism;
appropriate to the state of a somnambulist.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Whether this was an intentional and waking departure, or a
<qex>somnambulistic</qex> leave-taking and walking in her sleep, may
remain a subject of contention.</q> <rj><qau>Dickens.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Somne</ent>⟦br⟧
